snippet.title: Wreck-It Ralph Windows Phone gameplay
snippet.description: Sample gameplay of Wreck-It Ralph for Windows Phone.  This was recorded through a WP to PC video app.  However, the app only puts video onto the PC and not audio so the audio was recorded separately (which is the reason the audio quality is low).  The app also does not project the full resolution of the Windows Phone version due to USB bandwidth limitations.
